/**
 ** Simple XML syntax dictionary for TextMate.
 ** Author: Brian Lalor <blalor@bravo5.org>
 **
 ** Some patterns (and most colors) taken from the bundled HTML.plist.
 **
 ** $URL$
 ** $Id$
 **
 ** TODO
